---
/**
 * Visualizes the Claude Code → Codex migration flow as a horizontal SVG diagram.
 */
---
<figure class="migration-flow">
  <svg viewBox="0 0 880 320" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" role="img" aria-label="Claude Code에서 Codex로의 마이그레이션 흐름">
    <defs>
      <linearGradient id="grad-claude" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="100%">
        <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#f59e0b" />
        <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#d97706" />
      </linearGradient>
      <linearGradient id="grad-codex" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="100%">
        <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#10a37f" />
        <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#059669" />
      </linearGradient>
      <marker id="arrow" markerWidth="10" markerHeight="10" refX="8" refY="3" orient="auto">
        <path d="M0,0 L0,6 L9,3 z" fill="#94a3b8" />
      </marker>
    </defs>

    <!-- Claude Code side -->
    <g transform="translate(20,20)">
      <rect width="240" height="280" rx="14" fill="url(#grad-claude)" opacity="0.16" stroke="#f59e0b" stroke-width="1.5"/>
      <text x="120" y="32" text-anchor="middle" font-family="system-ui" font-size="18" font-weight="700" fill="#f59e0b">🟠 Claude Code</text>
      <g font-family="ui-monospace, monospace" font-size="12" fill="#e2e8f0">
        <rect x="16" y="56" width="208" height="34" rx="6" fill="#1e293b"/>
        <text x="28" y="78">CLAUDE.md</text>
        <rect x="16" y="100" width="208" height="34" rx="6" fill="#1e293b"/>
        <text x="28" y="122">.claude/settings.json</text>
        <rect x="16" y="144" width="208" height="34" rx="6" fill="#1e293b"/>
        <text x="28" y="166">.claude/skills/</text>
        <rect x="16" y="188" width="208" height="34" rx="6" fill="#1e293b"/>
        <text x="28" y="210">.claude/agents/</text>
        <rect x="16" y="232" width="208" height="34" rx="6" fill="#1e293b"/>
        <text x="28" y="254">claude /resume</text>
      </g>
    </g>

    <!-- Arrows -->
    <g stroke="#94a3b8" stroke-width="2" fill="none">
      <line x1="270" y1="92" x2="370" y2="92" marker-end="url(#arrow)"/>
      <line x1="270" y1="136" x2="370" y2="136" marker-end="url(#arrow)"/>
      <line x1="270" y1="180" x2="370" y2="180" marker-end="url(#arrow)"/>
      <line x1="270" y1="224" x2="370" y2="224" marker-end="url(#arrow)"/>
      <line x1="270" y1="268" x2="370" y2="268" marker-end="url(#arrow)"/>
    </g>

    <!-- Codex side -->
    <g transform="translate(380,20)">
      <rect width="240" height="280" rx="14" fill="url(#grad-codex)" opacity="0.16" stroke="#10a37f" stroke-width="1.5"/>
      <text x="120" y="32" text-anchor="middle" font-family="system-ui" font-size="18" font-weight="700" fill="#10a37f">🟢 Codex</text>
      <g font-family="ui-monospace, monospace" font-size="12" fill="#e2e8f0">
        <rect x="16" y="56" width="208" height="34" rx="6" fill="#1e293b"/>
        <text x="28" y="78">AGENTS.md</text>
        <rect x="16" y="100" width="208" height="34" rx="6" fill="#1e293b"/>
        <text x="28" y="122">~/.codex/config.toml</text>
        <rect x="16" y="144" width="208" height="34" rx="6" fill="#1e293b"/>
        <text x="28" y="166">.agents/skills/</text>
        <rect x="16" y="188" width="208" height="34" rx="6" fill="#1e293b"/>
        <text x="28" y="210">.codex/agents/*.toml</text>
        <rect x="16" y="232" width="208" height="34" rx="6" fill="#1e293b"/>
        <text x="28" y="254">codex resume</text>
      </g>
    </g>

    <!-- Notes -->
    <g transform="translate(640,20)" font-family="system-ui" font-size="11" fill="#cbd5e1">
      <rect width="220" height="280" rx="14" fill="#0f172a" stroke="#334155"/>
      <text x="14" y="28" font-weight="700" fill="#fbbf24">변환 시 주의</text>
      <text x="14" y="56">• 단순 이름 변경이 아님</text>
      <text x="14" y="76">• JSON → TOML 형식 변환</text>
      <text x="14" y="96">• Skills 경로는 .agents/skills/</text>
      <text x="14" y="116">  (NOT .codex/skills/)</text>
      <text x="14" y="140">• frontmatter 필드 대폭 축소</text>
      <text x="14" y="160">• UI/정책 → openai.yaml 분리</text>
      <text x="14" y="184">• Permissions → Approval +</text>
      <text x="14" y="200">  Sandbox 두 축으로 분해</text>
      <text x="14" y="224">• Hooks: features.codex_hooks</text>
      <text x="14" y="240">  활성화 게이트 필요</text>
      <text x="14" y="264">• 자세한 변환 절차는</text>
      <text x="14" y="280">  04, 05, 06 섹션 참조</text>
    </g>
  </svg>
  <figcaption>Claude Code의 핵심 자산을 Codex 생태계에 매핑하는 흐름. 모든 변환에는 형식·경로·필드 차이가 동반됩니다.</figcaption>
</figure>

<style>
.migration-flow {
  margin: 1.25rem 0;
  padding: 0.5rem;
  border-radius: 0.75rem;
  background: var(--sl-color-gray-7, #1e293b);
}
.migration-flow svg {
  width: 100%;
  height: auto;
  max-width: 880px;
  display: block;
  margin: 0 auto;
}
.migration-flow figcaption {
  margin-top: 0.5rem;
  font-size: 0.85rem;
  color: var(--sl-color-gray-3, #94a3b8);
  text-align: center;
  line-height: 1.5;
}
</style>
